  "question": "清朝的出现对于华夏文明是文化的断裂吗？",
  "author": "山高县",
  "content": "<p>其实圣朝官方意识形态，是马克思主义包装下的清朝经世致用学派。说清朝断裂文化，岂不是讽我圣朝传蛮夷之学?</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-8e5afb01ece18ca4802b5f9a78eae7f3_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"389\" data-rawheight=\"286\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-6627ac64d44e5282c088128b5b9d4a07_hd.jpg\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"389\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;389&#39; height=&#39;286&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"389\" data-rawheight=\"286\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-6627ac64d44e5282c088128b5b9d4a07_hd.jpg\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"389\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-8e5afb01ece18ca4802b5f9a78eae7f3_hd.jpg\"/></figure><p>回到话题，明王朝后继者的官方意识形态，如果不是理学的话，恐怕就是这些东东了:</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-cc1a0dafc2bb486f8431e7044ba6c596_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"290\" data-rawheight=\"220\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-c480b34c1608b1f0ec1d6ab145d68974_hd.jpg\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"290\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;290&#39; height=&#39;220&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"290\" data-rawheight=\"220\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-c480b34c1608b1f0ec1d6ab145d68974_hd.jpg\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"290\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-cc1a0dafc2bb486f8431e7044ba6c596_hd.jpg\"/></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-f25e6961927c9db6c77399fe74e674ec_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"850\" data-rawheight=\"407\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8ca18a58c1bc6989